fetchLatestQuery.string: SELECT * FROM @table WHERE _TABLE_SUFFIX BETWEEN FORMAT_DATE('%Y%m%d', DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE(), INTERVAL 7 DAY)) AND FORMAT_DATE('%Y%m%d', DATE_SUB(CURRENT_DATE(), INTERVAL 1 DAY)) AND event_timestamp + event_server_timestamp_offset >= @cursor

errNoId: Please provide an app id to search against
errNoCursor: Please provide a Unix timestamp in ms
errBadCursor: Cursor must be a Unix timestamp in ms
